<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Criteria for credit for AP performance may vary by field group, but no score lower than 4 will be considered for credit. AP credits are applied toward 32-course graduation requirement, but may not be used to satisfy an Educational Objective requirement. In general, AP credits do not apply to field of major requirements.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.pitzer.edu/admission/faqs.asp" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
